file.name: deviceasset-component.openapi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Device Asset Component
  description: Component
  version: 1.0.0

paths: {}

components:
  schemas:
    MultipleDeviceModel:
      required:
        - total
        - models
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        models:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceModel'
    SingleDeviceModel:
      required:
        - model
      properties:
        model:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceModel'
    DeviceModel:
      required:
        - id
        - name
        - resource_owner_id
        - created_at
        - updated_at
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        maker_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        version:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        watch:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Watch'
        components:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ConstitutionComponent'
        created_at:
          type: string
          description: ナノ秒
        updated_at:
          type: string
          description: ナノ秒
    DeviceModelRequest:
      required:
        - name
        - resource_owner_id
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        maker_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        version:
          type: string
        watch:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Watch'
        components:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ConstitutionComponent'
    DeviceModelUpdateRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        maker_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        version:
          type: string
        watch:
          type: object
          properties:
            types:
              type: object
              properties:
                unit:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    type: string
                parts:
                  items:
                    type: string
            component_ids:
              type: object
        components:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ConstitutionComponent'
    MultipleConstitutionComponent:
      type: object
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        components:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ConstitutionComponent'
    ConstitutionComponent:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        parent_id:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        address:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        type:
          $ref: './device-component.openapi.yml#/components/schemas/ComponentTypeEnum'
        attribute:
          nullable: true
          type: object
          example:
            model: RASOU001
            serialNo: 1234567890
            usage_start_date: 1575903600000000000
        display_info:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/DisplayInfo'
        components:
          nullable: true
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ConstitutionComponent'
    MultipleDeviceModelEntity:
      type: object
      required:
        - total
        - entities
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        entities:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceModelsEntity'
    SingleDeviceModelsEntity:
      type: object
      required:
        - entity
      properties:
        entity:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceModelsEntity'
    DeviceModelsEntity:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - device_id
        - key
        - model
        - resource_owner_id
        - created_at
        - updated_at
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        key:
          type: string
        device_id:
          type: string
        model:
          type: object
          required:
            - id
            - name
            - created_at
            - updated_at
          properties:
            id:
              type: string
            name:
              type: string
            key:
              type: string
            maker_id:
              type: string
            version:
              type: string
            created_at:
              type: string
              description: ナノ秒
            updated_at:
              type: string
              description: ナノ秒
        serial_number:
          type: string
        start_at:
          nullable: true
          type: string
          description: ナノ秒
        custom_inventory:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            example:
              001: bnu4hbnrmflais1m02e1
              002: bnu4hbnrmflais1m02e2
              003: bnu4hbnrmflais1m02e3
              004: bnu4hbnrmflais1m02e4
              005: bnu4hbnrmflais1m02e5
              006: bnu4hbnrmflais1m02e6
              007: bnu4hbnrmflais1m02e7
              008: bnu4hbnrmflais1m02e8
              009: bnu4hbnrmflais1m02e9
              010: bnu4hbnrmflais1m02e0
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
        watch:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Watch'
        components:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceEntitiesComponent'
        created_at:
          type: string
        updated_at:
          type: string
    MultipleDeviceEntitiesComponent:
      required:
        - total
        - components
      type: object
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        components:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceEntitiesComponent'
    SingleDeviceEntitiesComponent:
      type: object
      required:
        - component
      properties:
        component:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceEntitiesComponent'
    DeviceEntitiesComponent:
      type: object
      nullable: true
      required:
        - id
        - type
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        type:
          $ref: "./device-component.openapi.yml#/components/schemas/ComponentTypeEnum"
        parent_id:
          type: string
        attribute:
          type: object
        display_info:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/DisplayInfo'
        components:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceEntitiesComponent'
    DeviceEntitiesComponentUpdateRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
        parent_id:
          type: string
        attribute:
          type: object
          example:
            parts_id: parts0001
            serial_number: x00001
        display_info:
          $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/DisplayInfo'
    MultipleLifeCycle:
      type: object
      required:
        - total
        - lifecycles
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        lifecycles:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/LifeCycle'
    SingleLifeCycle:
      type: object
      required:
        - lifecycle
      properties:
        lifecycle:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/LifeCycle'

    LifeCycleRequest:
      type: object
      required:
        - event_at
        - event_kind
        - event_mode
        - event_type
      properties:
        event_kind:
          type: string
        event_mode:
          type: string
        event_type:
          type: string
        before_id:
          type: string
        before_component:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceEntitiesComponent'
        after_id:
          type: string
        after_component:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceEntitiesComponent'
        event_at:
          type: string
          description: ナノ秒
        note:
          type: string
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
    LifeCycle:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - event_at
        - event_kind
        - event_mode
        - event_type
        - resource_owner_id
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        event_kind:
          type: string
        event_mode:
          type: string
        event_type:
          type: string
        before_id:
          type: string
        before_component:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceEntitiesComponent'
        after_id:
          type: string
        after_component:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceEntitiesComponent'
        event_at:
          type: string
          description: ナノ秒
        note:
          type: string
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
    Watch:
      type: object
      nullable: true
      properties:
        types:
          nullable: true
          type: object
        component_ids:
          nullable: true
          type: object
          example:
            0x0010: [ "unitSerialNo", "unitStatus", "commandValue" ]
